<view class="container"><view class="tui-cmt-primary"><view class="tui-cmt-cell tui-cell-last"><view class="tui-header-box"><view class="tui-userinfo-box"><image class="tui-avatar" src="../../../static/images/news/avatar_1.jpg"></image><view class="tui-nickname-box"><view class="tui-cmt-nickname">米兰的卡先生</view><view class="tui-cmt-time">06-22 12:02</view></view></view><view class="{{(('tui-fabulous')+' '+(isFabulous?'tui-primary':''))}}" id="{{index}}" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['btnFabulous',['$event']]]]]}}" onTap="__e"><text>{{fabulous==0?'赞':fabulous}}</text><tui-icon vue-id="1" name="{{isFabulous?'agree-fill':'agree'}}" size="{{15}}" color="{{isFabulous?'#5677fc':'#9a9a9a'}}" onVueInit="__l"></tui-icon></view></view><view class="tui-cmt-content">我一直没懂赛前问一个主教练如何评价对手的主教练， 记者究竟是想得到什么答案？☺☺☺☺☺</view></view></view><view class="tui-empty"></view><view class="tui-cmt-title">全部回复（44）</view><view class="tui-cmtbox"><block a:for="{{replyList}}" a:for-item="item" a:for-index="index" a:key="index"><view class="tui-cmt-cell"><view class="tui-header-box"><view class="tui-userinfo-box"><image class="tui-avatar" src="{{'../../../static/images/news/'+item.avatar}}"></image><view class="tui-nickname-box"><view class="tui-cmt-nickname">{{item.nickname}}</view><view class="tui-cmt-time">{{item.time}}</view></view></view><view class="{{(('tui-fabulous')+' '+(item.isFabulous?'tui-primary':''))}}" id="{{index}}" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['cmtFabulous',['$event']]]]]}}" onTap="__e"><text>{{item.fabulous==0?'赞':item.fabulous}}</text><tui-icon vue-id="{{'2-'+index}}" name="{{item.isFabulous?'agree-fill':'agree'}}" size="{{15}}" color="{{item.isFabulous?'#5677fc':'#9a9a9a'}}" onVueInit="__l"></tui-icon></view></view><block a:if="{{item.reply.length>0}}"><view class="tui-reply-box"><block a:for="{{item.reply}}" a:for-item="items" a:for-index="index2" a:key="index2"><tui-list-cell vue-id="{{'3-'+index+'-'+index2}}" bgcolor="#f2f2f2" size="{{28}}" last="{{true}}" data-event-opts="{{[['^tap',[['cmtReply']]]]}}" onTap="__e" onVueInit="__l"><view class="tui-flex-1 tui-reply-nickname">{{items.nickname}}</view><view class="tui-flex-1">{{items.content}}</view></tui-list-cell></block></view></block><view class="tui-cmt-content">{{''+item.content+''}}</view></view></block></view><view class="tui-operation"><view class="tui-operation-inner"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['btnCmt',['$event']]]]]}}" class="tui-btn-comment" onTap="__e">回复楼主...</view></view></view><tui-loadmore vue-id="4" visible="{{loadding}}" index="{{3}}" type="primary" onVueInit="__l"></tui-loadmore><tui-nomore vue-id="5" visible="{{!pullUpOn}}" bgcolor="#fff" text="没有更多回复" onVueInit="__l"></tui-nomore><view class="tui-safearea-bottom"></view></view>